    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional, collector-grade vehicle that remains in showroom condition. The exterior paint retains a deep, mirror-like luster, free of any rock chips, swirl marks, or door dings, and has been professionally treated with a multi-year ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin is immaculate and remains smoke-free; the premium leather upholstery is supple with zero bolster wear, and the factory floor mats are in pristine condition. Every electronic feature, from the infotainment system to the heated seats, functions as if the car were brand new. Mechanically, this car is flawless, backed by a comprehensive, open-checkbook service history performed exclusively at authorized dealerships. It has been stored in a climate-controlled garage and driven only in fair weather. The sale includes all original keys, the owner\u2019s manual, and the original window sticker. This is a rare opportunity for a discerning buyer to acquire a perfectly preserved example that needs absolutely nothing.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
